body:
Sorry guys, I can't manage this topic anymore, it is just way too much. Every moment someone is posting their pic on this thread, but I can't add it to the topic, because it is just too much. It's been a great time. Someone new just post a Show Your Face Topic, and start a new trend there. Just keep in mind how much work it is...


Tips and Tricks!

- Easy Use of this thread: Use CTRL+F (Use CMD+F For Macs) to highlight certain words (To find someone's picture for example.) 
- Smile: Smile when you post a picture <3
- Stay Appropriate!: Don't say ; " 10/10 would bang " every time someone posts a pic.


The Story behind this Thread!

-I'll try to make this quick because most people on the forums hate reading... But basically I created this thread on the 10 november thinking it would be fun to share my face knowing I knew some of you for over 2 years. 
After its creation, the thread grew slowly and got 2000 views in 2 days which was normal for the time.

The thread was called "Show me your face? Pleaze! I did it <3".
A ton of players shared their picture but they were not being added on the main page until Alekpower made a huge mash-up and sorted all of the pictures in order. (JrMod at the time).

This post had about 20 pages when he first "mashed it" all up.

He managed it for a great amount of time until he had enough and said "Awarrior, im done, this is YOUR post".
Since then, im pretty much managing it, adding pictures when someone posts one so I dont have to go through 30 pages again.

And now its at 90 000 views... Jesus Christ.
Im also trying to keep this post alive by updating it frequently and adding various fun stuff

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
By the way, you can ask me anytime to remove your picture, if you wish so. 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Without further due, this is me and all the others who have showed their faces in order of appearance! Except for Funky, because...  it's Funky. We owe him all!
-Awarrior
